String substring() and replace() methods
==CODE==
import std.io.println;

String foo = "0123456789";

println(foo.substring(0,5));
println(foo.substring(5,6));
println(foo.replace("01234", "abcde"));

String bar = foo.substring(4,6).replace("456","foo").replace("789","bar");

println(bar);
==RESULT==
01234
56789
abcde56789
foobar
